sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as MCP client / AI session
    participant Tool as VsTools.bridge_get_tool_inventory
    participant Log as ILogger
    participant Inventory as IBridgeToolInventoryService
    participant Catalog as IBridgeToolCatalog
    participant Compiled as CompiledBridgeToolDiscovery
    participant MEF as MefBridgeToolDiscovery
    participant Snapshot as BridgeToolCatalogSnapshot

    Caller->>Tool: call bridge_get_tool_inventory
    Tool->>Log: start log with request id
    Tool->>Inventory: GetSnapshot()
    Inventory->>Catalog: GetTools()
    Catalog->>Compiled: DiscoverTools()
    Compiled-->>Catalog: compiled descriptors
    opt MEF directory discovery enabled by host configuration
        Catalog->>MEF: DiscoverTools()
        MEF-->>Catalog: MEF descriptors or empty result
    end
    Catalog-->>Inventory: descriptors only
    Inventory->>Snapshot: map manifest metadata and sort by tool id
    Snapshot-->>Tool: deterministic metadata snapshot
    Tool->>Log: completion log with request id, elapsed ms, tool count
    Tool-->>Caller: metadata-only JSON snapshot

    Note over Tool,Snapshot: No bridge tool ExecuteAsync call occurs during inventory.
    Note over Tool,Caller: The diagnostic does not send pipe requests, invoke ChatEngine, trigger approval, or expose raw payloads/secrets.
    Note over Catalog,MEF: Empty or missing MEF discovery remains safe and produces an empty descriptor contribution.
